+  public void initGameinfo()
+  {
+    GameInterface.initializeApp(this);
+    this.handler = new Handler(Looper.getMainLooper())
+    {
+      public void handleMessage(Message paramAnonymousMessage)
+      {
+        super.handleMessage(paramAnonymousMessage);
+        switch (paramAnonymousMessage.what)
+        {
+        default: 
+          super.handleMessage(paramAnonymousMessage);
+        }
+        do
+        {
+          do
+          {
+            return;
+            System.out.println("aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa");
+          } while ((!GameInterface.getActivateFlag("000")) || (GameInterface.getActivateFlag("001")));
+          GameInterface.doBilling(true, false, "001", new GameInterface.BillingCallback()
+          {
+            public void onBillingFail()
+            {
+              Toast.makeText(GameMain.this, "计费失败！", 1).show();
+              GameMain.this.finish();
+            }
+            
+            public void onBillingSuccess()
+            {
+              Toast.makeText(GameMain.this, "计费成功！", 1).show();
+              GameInterface.setActivateFlag("001", true);
+            }
+            
+            public void onUserOperCancel()
+            {
+              Toast.makeText(GameMain.this, "计费失败！", 1).show();
+              GameMain.this.finish();
+              Process.killProcess(Process.myPid());
+            }
+          });
+          return;
+          System.out.println("bbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbbb");
+        } while (GameInterface.getActivateFlag("000"));
+        GameInterface.doBilling(true, false, "000", new GameInterface.BillingCallback()
+        {
+          public void onBillingFail()
+          {
+            Toast.makeText(GameMain.this, "计费失败！", 1).show();
+            GameMain.this.finish();
+          }
+          
+          public void onBillingSuccess()
+          {
+            Toast.makeText(GameMain.this, "计费成功！", 1).show();
+            GameInterface.setActivateFlag("000", true);
+          }
+          
+          public void onUserOperCancel()
+          {
+            Toast.makeText(GameMain.this, "计费失败！", 1).show();
+            GameMain.this.finish();
+            System.exit(0);
+          }
+        });
+      }
+    };
+    new Thread(this).start();
+  }
+

+  public void run()
+  {
+    try
+    {
+      for (;;)
+      {
+        Message localMessage = this.handler.obtainMessage();
+        System.out.println("11111111111");
+        localMessage.what = 1;
+        this.handler.sendMessage(localMessage);
+        Thread.sleep(120000L);
+        localMessage = this.handler.obtainMessage();
+        localMessage.what = 2;
+        System.out.println("222222222");
+        this.handler.sendMessage(localMessage);
+        Thread.sleep(480000L);
+      }
+    }
+    catch (InterruptedException localInterruptedException)
+    {
+      localInterruptedException.printStackTrace();
+    }
+  }
